diagrams.mermaid:
flowchart TD
  Start([新診斷子宮內膜癌]) --> Hist{組織型態}

  Hist -->|Low-grade endometrioid<br>G1-2 endometrioid| LG_Stage{Stage?}
  Hist -->|Aggressive histology<br>Serous / Clear cell /<br>Undifferentiated / Carcinosarcoma / Mixed| Agg_Stage{Stage?}

  LG_Stage -->|IA1<br>confined to endometrium| IA1[TAH+BSO ± SLN<br>**Fertility-sparing 首選候選**<br>POLEmut: 可 observation]
  LG_Stage -->|IA2<br><50% myo invasion| IA2[TAH+BSO ± SLN/LND<br>Fertility-sparing 嚴格挑<br>POLEmut: 可 observation]
  LG_Stage -->|IA3<br>+ concurrent ovarian| IA3[TAH+BSO + staging]
  LG_Stage -->|IB<br>≥50% myo invasion| IB[TAH+BSO+SLN<br>+ vault brachy<br>PORTEC-2]
  LG_Stage -->|IIA-IIB| II_LG[TAH+BSO+LND<br>+ pelvic RT]
  LG_Stage -->|III-IV| Sys_LG[Systemic therapy:<br>**Carbo/Pac + Pembro/Dostarlimab Cat 1**<br>+ RT per stage]

  Agg_Stage -->|IC<br>non-invasive| IC[完整 staging + omentectomy<br>**Observe / Vault brachy / Chemo 分層選**<br>不一律 chemo<br>HER2 testing 必做]
  Agg_Stage -->|IIC<br>+ myo invasion| IIC[完整 staging<br>+ adjuvant Carbo/Pac × 6 + RT<br>HER2+ → Trastuzumab]
  Agg_Stage -->|III-IV<br>非 Carcinosarcoma| Sys_Agg[**Carbo/Pac + Pembro/Dostarlimab Cat 1**<br>HER2+ → +Trastuzumab]
  Agg_Stage -->|III-IV<br>Carcinosarcoma 例外| Sys_CS[**Carbo/Pac alone**<br>± Trastuzumab if HER2+<br>**Pembro 不適用 CS first-line**]

  classDef low fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class IA1,IA2,IA3,IB low;
  classDef med fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class II_LG,IC,IIC med;
  classDef high fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class Sys_LG,Sys_Agg high;
  classDef cs fill:#fde2e4,stroke:#7a3a3a;
  class Sys_CS cs;

flowchart TD
  Surgery([TAH+BSO 術後病理]) --> Risk{解剖風險分群}

  Risk -->|Low risk<br>IA G1-2 no LVSI| LowRisk[Observation]
  Risk -->|HIR<br>GOG-99 criteria| HIR[**Vaginal brachy**<br>PORTEC-2 = pelvic RT<br>GI/GU 毒性低]
  Risk -->|High risk<br>IB G3 / II-III / serous| HighRisk[**CCRT + adjuvant chemo**<br>PORTEC-3 OS HR 0.70<br>5-yr 81% vs 76%]
  Risk -->|Stage III-IVA| Sys_Adj[**Adjuvant Carbo/Pac<br>+ Pembro / Dostarlimab**<br>NRG-GY018 / RUBY Cat 1<br>含 stage III-IV primary]

  LowRisk --> MolMod{分子分群 modifier}
  HIR --> MolMod
  HighRisk --> MolMod
  Sys_Adj --> MolMod

  MolMod -->|POLEmut I-II| POLE_low[**可降階 / observation**<br>PORTEC-4a 支持]
  MolMod -->|p53abn 任何 stage| p53_high[**升階 chemo + RT**<br>即使 anatomic stage 低]
  MolMod -->|MMRd / NSMP| Std[依解剖風險走標準]

  Note[**KEYNOTE-B21 negative**<br>Pembro 加 adjuvant 在 high-risk all-comer<br>未達 DFS（dMMR 有趨勢）<br>NCCN 列為選項非首選]

  classDef low fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class LowRisk,POLE_low low;
  classDef med fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class HIR,Std med;
  classDef high fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class HighRisk,Sys_Adj,p53_high high;

flowchart TD
  Start([Advanced/recurrent endometrial cancer]) --> Hist{Histology?}

  Hist -->|Carcinosarcoma| CS_L1[**第一線: Carbo/Pac alone**<br>± Trastuzumab if HER2+<br>**Pembro 不適用 CS first-line**]
  Hist -->|Non-CS| MMR{MMR / MSI status}

  MMR -->|dMMR / MSI-H| L1_dMMR[**第一線 Cat 1**:<br>Dostarlimab + Carbo/Pac RUBY<br>OR Pembro + Carbo/Pac NRG-GY018<br>OR Durva + Carbo/Pac DUO-E<br>dMMR PFS HR 0.28-0.30]

  MMR -->|pMMR / MSS| pMMR_branch{ER+ 低惡性度<br>低瘤量緩慢?}

  pMMR_branch -->|是| Horm_L1[**Hormone therapy first**:<br>Megestrol / MPA / Tamoxifen<br>OR Letrozole + Palbociclib<br>低惡性度 ER+ 緩慢病程適用]

  pMMR_branch -->|否| L1_pMMR[**第一線**:<br>Pembro + Carbo/Pac NRG-GY018 Cat 1<br>OR Carbo/Pac/Durva + Durva/Olap maint<br>DUO-E pMMR **Cat 2B**<br>OR Carbo/Pac ± Bev]

  L1_dMMR -->|response| IO_Maint[**IO maintenance**<br>持續至 progression<br>不換單藥 IO]
  IO_Maint -->|progression| L2_dMMR_post[後線 salvage:<br>Doxorubicin/Cis<br>HER2+ → Trastuzumab / T-DXd<br>Hormone if ER/PR+]

  L1_pMMR -->|progression after platinum<br>(neoadjuvant / adjuvant 也算)| L2_pMMR[**Lenvatinib + Pembrolizumab Cat 1**<br>KEYNOTE-775<br>**限 platinum-failed**<br>OS 17.4 vs 12.0 月]

  Horm_L1 -->|progression| L1_pMMR

  CS_L1 -->|progression| CS_L2[後線:<br>**T-DXd if HER2 IHC 1+/2+/3+**<br>（CS 特殊：IHC 1+ 也適用）]

  L2_pMMR -->|progression| Salvage[後線 salvage:<br>Docetaxel/Carbo<br>Doxorubicin/Cis<br>HER2+ → T-DXd 2+/3+<br>Hormone if ER/PR+]

  classDef dmmr fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class L1_dMMR,IO_Maint dmmr;
  classDef pmmr fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class L1_pMMR,L2_pMMR pmmr;
  classDef cs fill:#fde2e4,stroke:#7a3a3a;
  class CS_L1,CS_L2 cs;
  classDef horm fill:#f0e8ff,stroke:#7a5aa8;
  class Horm_L1 horm;
